        <item>
            <title>【MWC 2024】Lenovo 展示透明手提电脑，荧幕通透、亮度可达 1000 尼特</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/lenovo-mwc-2024/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-mwc-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/lenovo-mwc-2024/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 10:30:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lenovo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Micro LED]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221500</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Lenovo 今日在世界流动通讯大会（Mobile World Congress，MWC）展示了一款极具未来感的手提电脑，配备 17.3 吋 Micro-LED 透明显示器，为用家提供完全无边框、透明的显示体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221519" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/0416-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/0416-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/0416-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这款手提电脑最主要的卖点是其配备无边框 17.3 吋 MicroLED 萤幕。如用户没有开启手提电脑时，其透明度达 55%，而手提电脑萤幕的透明度会随著萤幕亮度提升而下降，峰值亮度达 1000 尼特时用家会看到完全不透明的萤幕。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221527" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/780e5be9527e92c-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/780e5be9527e92c-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/780e5be9527e92c.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这款手提电脑有趣之处是其能够融合虚拟及现实。LENOVO 表示，这款手提电脑使用 AIGC 人工智能生成内容，透明萤幕能够与实体物件互动并叠加数码资讯，为用户创造独特的使用体验，从而开辟全新工作模式。手提电脑的透明萤幕可以融入各式各样的环境，用户能够使用专用轻触笔在键盘及绘图版之间无缝切换。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221526" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ddfea2ef98a51aa-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ddfea2ef98a51aa-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ddfea2ef98a51aa.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>透明萤幕或会引起用家关注私隐问题， LENOVO 就表示这个萤幕可以调节其透明度，让用户在不同时候切换不同透明度，以此提升用户的使用体验。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.lenovo.com/pressroom/press-releases/lenovos-cutting-edge-thinkpad-and-thinkbook-laptops-pave-the-way-for-ai-pc-innovation-at-mwc/">LENOVO</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/08/lenovo-legion-go-review/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Lenovo Legion Go　外形　手感　效能　打机体验　散热　特别功能　屏幕　音效开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/28/lenovo-legion-9i-first-review/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Lenovo Legion 9i　外形　手感　功能　打机表现　硬件配置初步评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/11/2023-tablet-sales-drop/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">平板电脑年销量下跌   iPad 仍然市占最高</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/lenovo-mwc-2024/notebook/">【MWC 2024】Lenovo 展示透明手提电脑，荧幕通透、亮度可达 1000 尼特</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
